name: EXPLODED VIEWS OF A FUTURE PRESENT_DRONEv1.2
description: In an exploded view, all parts of an object are visible. It was used for the first time Marino Taccola and popularised by Leonardo Da Vinci. Frederik De Wilde combines exploded views and machine learning in a contemporary statement about optimisation. Colour shifting edition. Artwork by Frederik De Wilde. 1920x1080, MP4, Audio, @Studio_De_Wilde
